physical_examinations.relevant_findings: At age 20 yr, noted to have a round face, deep and hoarse voice, generalized acanthosis nigricans, skin tags, cysts in axillary and pubic regions, severe lipodystrophy with muscle and labia majora pseudohypertrophy, prominent veins, absence of gluteal fat, hirsutism, and Cushingoid habitus.

At age 26 yr, noted to have a round face, mild nuchal acanthosis nigricans, skin tags, severe lipodystrophy with muscle pseudohypertrophy, prominent veins, absence of gluteal fat, and hirsutism. Her lipodystrophy phenotype was less severe than that of proband 1.
